thread.title: Sue Rogers

author: Sue Rogers
title: Sue Rogers
text:
All 3 of my dogs got cancer. I decided to make my own dog food with people grade products and all natural supplements. I started using UpCo bone meal several months ago. Bone meal was recommended as an additive by my vet.
I have been buying this product from Amazon but was unable to get it when I needed it. I decided to check out the supplier's website. Turned out to be cheaper than Amazon so I will be ordering direct from now on.
